content.detailedDescription: Was on top 14,000f mt evans taking meteorite pics. camera (nikom d7100) set up to take a sequence of 9 13second exposures while on tripod. i just pointed camera to some part of sky for each 9pic sequence. i took over 500 pics. i didn't notice object until today when reviewing pics. i am submitting two pics. the first is #8 of a sequence which does not show the object (for comparison). the 2nd is #9. during the 13 second exposure you see a light from left to right and on the right, above a bright star, you see the object. you probably should zoom in.  because the line is not straight i ruled out a meteorite, satellite or airplane. i did crop the original photos and you see about 1/4th of each pic. the object looks like no other i have ever seen. note - my asa on camera was set to 1600. please give me your evaluation in this. thanks ahead of time.

content.detailedDescription: A little after 10 pm, i was outside having a smoke when i saw a bright fire ball in the sky. after walking to my driveway, to try and get a closer look, i looked to my right (eastward) and saw about 4 more objects. at first they were in a straight line, but then moved into a triangular shape and one by one disappeared. after about 6 minutes the last one appeared and i followed it on camera until that one to vanished! there had to be close to 20 different orbs that would appear out of nowhere, fly quickly. i was in awe, i couldn't move, barely able to breath because i had no idea what was going on. i couldn't even call my family to see what was happening. about 5 minutes after the last orb disappeared, a tremendous lighting/thunder storm came in. sorry about the quality, i tried zooming in and out numerous times!
content.summary: Over 20 orbs appear, and vanish

content.detailedDescription:
On july 11, 2013, i was living in a small village called afterlee in the nsw northern rivers, approximately 80 kilometres west of the gold coast, australia. a little before 6pm, i went outside to photograph clouds, a common occurrence for me, as i was a member of a cloud photography group on facebook.

just a shade before 6pm, looking to the horizon to the nw, i spotted a distant cylindrical shaped object that appeared be to be tumbling upwards.

i thought at first it may be a satellite, but every satellite i've seen has moved in a straight line. the course of this object was erratic.

the object appeared to the eye as a glinting silver object, but close ups of subsequent photographs revealed a red streak in the centre of the object. it was first spotted around 20 degrees above the horizon, and as i snapped my pictures, it moved upwards in a distinctive, end over end tumbling motion to about 40 degrees or so before i lost sight of it. it just seemed to disappear.

at first i was simply puzzled, but really had no time for any emotive reaction. i just zoomed, focused and snapped. the camera, a canon 1100d was set for continuous, so i just kept the button down and held the camera as steady as possible while looking through the viewfinder. when i processed the images to my computer, i was pretty sure that i'd caught something unusual.

after a total of approximately 30 to 35 seconds, the craft simply vanished.
content.summary: Distant cigar shaped craft photographed (11 images) tumbling upwards on erratic course, at afterlee, nsw australia

content.detailedDescription: August 12th 2016 was probably one of the scariest and most fascinating days of my life. it was the day i saw something unexplainable, unnatural, and utterly amazing. it all started at around 11 o'clock that night, when i was laying in my bed, unable to sleep. i had been tossing and turning since 10, because my house was so hot i couldn't sleep. i had a fan on the right side of my bed, but thought i would be cooler if i had one in my right side, too. so i went into my sisters room to get her extra fan she keeps in between her bed and nightstand. i walked in her room and went to get the fan, but stopped when i saw a tiny white light out of her south-west facing window. coming up from behind the horizon was a tiny white light, a little bit bigger than a star, but smaller than a planet. i knew from first glance that this was not a satellite or airplane. it was rising in an almost squiggly motion, and it was hitting each star on its way up. almost like a connect the dots, although it left no trail. it kept getting closer, and as it came clearer into view, i saw two smaller white lights following the big white light on either side, and together the formed a triangle. the figures were now almost overhead at treetop level,  and all of a sudden, two small rainbow rays of light shown out from either side of the main figure. it then sped up and disappeared above my house. i have absolutely no idea what this could have been. i was too astonished to remember to take any pictures/videos, but believe me, i am so mad at myself that i didn't. i would do anything just to see it one more time. whatever it was, it was very close to landing on earth.
content.summary: I saw a small white light swirling in the sky with rainbow beams coming out.

content.detailedDescription:
I was standing in my back yard observing distant storm clouds in the east around 1925 on july 25th 2016.
at this time, i caught a gimps of a bright object just beyond the trees to my east and at first i thought it may be a bright satellite which would have been impressive for that time of the day.
we also live within a flight path so i thought it could be a plane.
as it cleared the biggest tree and came into view, i could tell that it was not a plane, was to low to be a satellite and to slow as well.It looked to be within 5 miles away and from my prospective,just above the trees as the pictures will show.
i continued to watch as it traveled in a straight line from approx. the north east to the south and eventually lost sight when it was obscured by more trees in my line of sight.
the reason i report now is because i had forgotten that i did take some pictures and hope that at a minimum, someone may be able to enhance them enough to make out what this may be.
i wish i had a better story to tell but that is about it. i know what satellites look like, planes, helicopters, stars, chinese lanterns and drones. i can honestly say that i am baffled by this and "thankfully"
i had the sense enough to take a series of pictures.
the first photo is of the area of the observation.
photos 2-4 are in order and show the object and path.
i have geo. location and time date stamp on the photos.

about 2.5 years ago i witnessed a similar object with the same characteristics while on the roof at work in the city of syracuse.
the same distance away, the same height in the sky the same speed, it was on a east to west path at approx. 2100 hours in september or october.
unfortunately i did not have the sense of mind to take pictures, i was just surprised and mesmerized and thought no one would believe this and forgot about until now.
if this turns out to be something of this earth, then i am sorry to waist your time. thank you for looking into this..
content.summary: Star like object that stayed on a straight path that had a variable bright orange/yellow glow that traveled slow.

content.detailedDescription: I was standing outside my in-laws fence smoking a cigarette. i was looking at the stars just thinking when it just appeared at about the 10 o'clock position. at first i thought it was a plane as it continued straight, once it started to weave until about the 1 o'clock position then continued straight then shot off and the 2 o'clock position i was in awe trying to figure it out. the crafts altitude seemed to be higher than commercial flights but was lower that satellites. from where i was standing it was super bright and i couldn't tell the body of the craft but the light changed from orb to cylinder (like you flatten a balloon halfway). after it disappeared i went inside and told my wife because she asked what was wrong because i apparently looked "nervous"
content.summary: Ufo appeared had unusual flight pattern then disappeared

content.detailedDescription: We were traveling to albuquerque, nm and we stopped at the rest stop, just east of ne nm/az border, to use the facilities. my wife was driving when we arrived at the rest stop and i had been taking pictures of the scenery nearby along the way. after stopping, i took a few more pictures with my cell phone. the sun was directly above us(as you can see by the shadows below the trees) and it was hard to get a good look at the pictures with the glare from the sun. when we reached our final destination, in albuquerque, i uploaded the pictures from my phone to the computer to see how the photos came out. i noticed something reflective in one of the pictures and wondered what it was because the sun had been directly above when i took the pic. i enlarged the photo and i was stunned to see that it was a metallic looking object with no wings, propellers or rotors. i never saw the object with my eyes. i wasn't taking a picture of a ufo it just appeared in the picture. about a year later, in august of 2015, i read in the paper that there was a mufon symposium nearby in rio rancho, nm, where i now live. i went there, waited patiently (for 2 hours) to show the presenter my photo. he seemed unimpressed and i was disappointed. i've often thought about reporting it but, until now, felt that if the guy from mufon was unimpressed then who would be. i still don't know what this was and no one i've shown the picture to can figure it out either. i would love to hear from someone at mufon about this. my wife was with me when i took the photo but saw nothing as well.
content.summary: Appeared in one of several picture i took of the area

content.detailedDescription: This event actually happened to my son-in-law. we were having lunch when he said he got some strange photographs. earlier in the day, he was canoeing on middle waterton lake, and was taking pictures of the scenery. later, when he looked at the pictures, he saw a green orb in them. he had taken a series of eight photos, and in this series the orb first appeared just above the surface of the lake, then rose about 20 feet in the air, then descended again to the surface of the lake. we all looked closely at the photos, expecting it was a refraction in the lens or some other explainable phenomena, but it just couldn't be explained. he is a mechanical engineer, and even he is mystified. he has agreed to allow us to submit this report as his first reaction is that he captured photos of a ufo!
content.summary: A small glowing kidney shaped orb, green in colour, floating above lake surface, rose in the air about 20 feet, then descended back to lake surface.

content.detailedDescription:
Three of us were on a road in a car in northern ontario, canada. we looked up to our left it was hovering over the trees. we stopped. my sister and boyfriend exited the car to look at it. i was terrified and stayed in the passenger seat.
it was a cylindrical object. it was hovering silently just above the trees approximately 50 feet away from us. there was no mistaking it for anything else. it was huge, approximately 200-300 feet wide. it had lights.  it hovered for approximately 2 minutes. it then flew away with absolutely no noise so fast that it disappeared within a second.

my sister and boyfriend were awed. i was terrified.

still hate driving at night because of this.
content.summary: Very large ufo circular, lights, hovered over trees then took off in a milisecond

content.detailedDescription: Myself and my two kids were swimming. it was a cloudless night and we could see many different stars of varying brightness. i spotted the light traveling from the northwest towards the southeast. it was similar in size and color to many of the dimmer stars (light blue). however, it was not distorted or flickering like a star. it was at a cloud level altitude and moving at a speed similar to a small airplane. i jokingly told my kids to look and i said " ok kids, lets see if this is an airplane or ufo, if it is a plane we should see blinking lights and it will continue straight, but if it is a ufo it may take a sharp turn". possibly out of boredom, we watched it continue in a straight path, but it never had a blinking light and remained at a steady pace. suddenly it stopped, we all were shocked...But then it changed to a solid white light and it appeared to shrink and then disappear. we were stunned and my youngest got scared...But we searched the sky in a panic to see if it was just our eyes and that it may show up again in the same path. a few moments later a white streak of light flashed to the right of us...It appeared to be almost on top of us. it was only a blink and had my son not seen it also and gasped, i may have not believed it. we searched the sky, but nothing was moving...And there were no clouds. we did not see anything else, and my youngest demanded we go inside.
content.summary: Star looki light (blueish-not flickering) airplane speed/altitude across the sky,straight line for 40 seconds, stopped,changed to a smaller white light and vanished,cloudless night. 10 sec later bright flash above us

content.detailedDescription: My family and i are on vacation, and i'm writing this just after witnessing a very strange light that flew slowly over us after we started heading back to our hotel room for the night, we were playing at the school's playground with our two little kids and it was getting dark. there was a beautiful pink sunset and we were looking at mt. adams, pointing out contrails over the mountain in the sunset. only a few stars were starting to show since the sun had set, and from where we were standing looking up a light appeared and was flying pretty steadily, soundless, no contrail, no blinky lights, not shaped like a helicopter or an airplane, and it was as bright as maybe 5 bright stars put together. we didn't really have any clouds in the sky because its a hot summer night and i'm pretty sure it isn't a satellite or the space station because of it's brightness. we had our camera to take pictures of the kids and we started to take a few photos and see if anything would show because it was getting darker. i uploaded them and zoomed into a few of them. one of the pictures is very odd looking. i bet if somebody could alter the raw pictures they might be able to notice something better than i can. i did notice in a few of the pictures reddish glow around one side of the object, purple, and blue. i only saw bright whiteish yellow with the naked eye. this thing flew directly above our heads maybe a few miles up? not sure on the distance. we watched it for a good 5 mins and then it kept flying and went behind trees, we followed to see it some more but after we came to the other side we didn't see it flying anymore. we have the moon in a few of the pictures for size reference. i zoomed in on the first picture and it looks really weird, if you zoom in on them all and i have more to submit they are all different. this is strange and i'd like to know if anyone else knows what this is.
content.summary: Mt. adams family playing at school playground and talking about ufos and a bright white light flew slowly over us and disappeared. pictures show something strange

content.detailedDescription: My daughter & i had just arrived home at around 10:00 to 10:30, we pulled into our driveway which runs east-west. she's out of the car and says look up ! i look west over the top of our garage, thinking there would be a meteor, but instead i see what looks like an object in the sky on fire, but there's no sound, i keep watching, and there are some neighbors getting into their car about 45 ft away & i ask them to look up, i had to back out on ft so they could see what direction i was pointing and the they saw what we saw , what looked like some sort of flying craft  on fire, then it steadily turned south, that's when i/we observed the flame disappear to the far side of the object then as the flame disappeared, the craft became like either invisible, or it matched the background of the sky,we could not see anything moving nor could we hear anything in the sky at all...We just stared up at the sky wondering what it was that we just saw, when a the sudden there north of where we last saw the object disappear there was a big black blob of what looked like a deflated black balloon descend to the earth...Neighbors thought it fell into my back yard, but i knew the distance was greater than that and i took them into my back yard to prove to them that whatever just fell to earth was farther awy than it looked...And of the neighbors had his ph with him, but i don't know what he got if anything on his ph camera...
content.summary: Low slow silent headed e & it was like it was on fire, no sound,,then it turned s, & you could still see the flame like light on its far side as it went sth from east, once the flame was on the far side away from our visual, youcouldnt

content.detailedDescription: I looked out my patio screen door (it's a cool summer night) and saw solid white and red lights. the craft was going way too fast to be a plane, after about 5 seconds it flashed red and then disappeared. i saw it while on my couch. it was night time with clear skies, not a single cloud in sight. i immediately got up and went on the patio to verify if it was an actual ufo or a plane by looking up to see if i saw any other lights to compare. i counted 4 very slow moving craft consistently flashing a red and either a white or green light (im thinking white) and determined those were completely different from what i had seen. the craft i was seeing when i went onto the patio was very small, equivilant to a star (i determined them to be airplanes), and the craft i saw disappear would be equivelant to the size of a penny from where i had been seated.
content.summary: Fast flying disappearing ufo

content.detailedDescription: Hi me and my wife both had a close up encounter with a intelligent blue orb like thing that flew in to our house then out thru the walls and back in then flew right up to my face at amazing speeds ,then it flew off and we watched it go through the walls without leaving a trace or even no damage to my walls,it was the most amazing thing i have seen and the color was the best blue i have ever seen,  about a week later i was sitting up late at night and i heard a strange noise that ive never heard before, then about a min later i saw a net like device that was the same blue color to the orb ,it came right thru my ceiling at about half way up the house and extended itself till my whole downstairs was lit up by this net, it stayed there for about 30 seconds then the blue net started to withdraw, the whole time this was happening a bright white light was coming thru my back kitchen window and door ,i had a terrible feeling that i was being scanned or something in my own home, i thought i was about to get abducted ,ive been regularly seeing strange ufos around my property since, im worried about my 4 kids safety and my wifes aswell as my own after what ive seen. ive started to come up in round blisters since and my doctor is even baffled by whats causing these blister like spots all over my body.Ever since this has happend i feel like whenever i go to sleep im being contacted in my dreams which is really weird, i feel like im being prepared for something with the visions i keep recieving ,sorry i took so long to repot this set of incidents but ive been trying to make sense out of my situation and i even tried to forget about it but it just wont go away so thats why im getting in touch now
content.summary: Close encounter with orb that flew in and out my house multiple times in about a min ,then a week later i was sitting up watching tv when i heard a loud metal like object that soundedlike nothing ive heard before then a blue net came thru the walls

content.detailedDescription: My wife had gone to a convience store in alberta and returned to her car when was talking to her when looked up toward the north and noticed tbis object in the sky.A white looking object with what looked like windoows. she happened to take 2 photos of the object before it took off.

content.detailedDescription: I was sitting on my back porch watching the start of the persied meteor shower, when i was scanning the night sky for meteors. i noticed almost all the meteors moving in a southerly direction, looking straight up from my seat i noticed an arrow shaped object that appeared to be decending from high altitude with red orange leading edge with vorticies off each tip of the triangle shaped craft and moving at a high rate of speed, at least as fast as the meteors i had been watching , but moving in the opposite direction, moving south to north. i estimate the craft had just entered our atmosphere and was close to a mile across.
content.summary: Craft triangular in shape not showing lights glowing red orange on leading edge
